  "monster": {
    "title": "Miezarch.",
    "body": "One of the many lords of Pandemonium, Miezarch has a muscular red body with large, powerful wings and eerily human features. It seems utterly heartbroken.\n\n<lightgrey>Max HP: 195     </lightgrey><lightgrey> Will: +++      </lightgrey><lightgrey>   AC: ++++     </lightgrey><lightgrey>  EV: +         </lightgrey>                \n<lightgrey>    rF: ∞       </lightgrey><lightgrey>   rC: ++.      </lightgrey><lightgrey>rPois: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>rNeg: ∞         </lightgrey><lightgrey>rElec: +        </lightgrey>\n<lightgrey>Threat: High    </lightgrey><lightgrey>Class: Demonic  </lightgrey><lightgrey> Size: Large    </lightgrey><lightgrey> Int: Human     </lightgrey>\n\n\nYou have about 79% to hit with the fire staff of Defence by Offence and 79% to hit with your pseudopods.\nIt has about 69% to hit you.\n\nAttack              Max Damage  \nHit: chaotic touch  40 + chaos  \n\nIt is immune to torment; and resistant to miasma.\nIt is vulnerable to silver and hated by Zin.\nIt can see invisible.\nIt can fly.\nIt can open doors.\nSPELLSET_PLACEHOLDERTo read a description, press the key listed above. (AdB) indicates damage (the sum of A B-sided dice), (x%) indicates the chance to defeat your Will, and (y) indicates the spell range; shown in red if you are in range.\n\nIt is currently targeted by:\n  your fire vortex\n  your fire vortex\n  your fire vortex\n  your fire vortex\n  your fire vortex",
